A warm, golden-hour photorealistic image of a serene ancient stone Buddha statue face in close-up, partially covered with soft green moss and delicate flowering vines, surrounded by the misty atmosphere of an overgrown temple garden in Southeast Asia. Morning light filters through tropical foliage, casting dappled shadows across the Buddha's peaceful, weathered features. Dewdrops cling to nearby lotus leaves in the foreground, while faint incense smoke curls upward in soft wisps. The expression radiates profound tranquility and timeless compassion, with eyes half-closed in meditation. Rich earthy tones of amber, sage green, and warm terracotta dominate the palette, creating an atmosphere of sacred stillness and natural harmony.
